graph TB
    subgraph "Notebook Controller Component"
        NotebookReconciler[Notebook Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        CullingReconciler[Culling Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbe[Health Probe<br/>:8081/TCP HTTP]

        NotebookReconciler -->|exposes| MetricsServer
        NotebookReconciler -->|exposes| HealthProbe
        CullingReconciler -->|exposes| MetricsServer
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler

    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| StatefulSet[StatefulSet]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>notebook-name<br/>80/TCP to 8888]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService]

    StatefulSet -->|manages| NotebookPod[Notebook Pod<br/>Jupyter Server<br/>8888/TCP]

    CullingReconciler -->|queries /api/kernels| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|adds culling annotation| NotebookCR

    NotebookReconciler -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    VirtualService -->|routes traffic via| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>Optional]

    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional] -->|scrapes| MetricsServer

    style NotebookReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style CullingReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style MetricsServer fill:#7ed321
    style HealthProbe fill:#7ed321
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623
    style StatefulSet fill:#f5a623
    style Service fill:#f5a623
    style VirtualService fill:#f5a623
    style NotebookPod fill:#9013fe
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8
    style IstioGateway fill:#e8e8e8
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8
